=============================================================
Create Database and Schemas
=============================================================
Script Purpose:
    This script creates a new database named 'DataWarehouse'.
    Additionally, the script sets up three schemas  within the database: 'bronze', 'silver', and 'gold' for organise our projects .


USE master;
GO


-- Create the 'DataWarehouse' database
CREATE DATABASE DataWarehouse;
GO

USE DataWarehouse;
GO

-- Create Schemas
CREATE SCHEMA bronze;
GO

CREATE SCHEMA silver;
GO

CREATE SCHEMA gold;
GO
